headline: Is It Time To Reassess Intuit After Its Recent AI Innovation Push?
summary: If you are wondering whether Intuit is still worth buying at current levels, or if most of the upside is already priced in, you are not alone. That is exactly what we are going to unpack here. After a strong multi year run, with the stock up 78.4% over 3 years and 84.2% over 5 years, recent moves have been more modest, with gains of 2.2% over the last week, 1.3% over the last month, and 7.7% year to date, while sitting only 0.6% higher than a year ago.
